{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-11",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_11_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Fat Man",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 484.12,
  "page_end_sec": 724.44,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.574,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 484.12,
      "end": 487.76,
      "text": "The fat man raised his glass and held it against a window's light.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 488.18,
      "end": 491.14,
      "text": "He nodded approvingly at the bubbles running up in it."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.28,
      "end": 492.0,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.18,
      "end": 492.5,
      "text": "\"Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.54,
      "end": 492.76,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.94,
      "end": 494.48,
      "text": "here's to plain speaking"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.74,
      "end": 495.72,
      "text": "and clear understanding.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 496.96,
      "end": 498.42,
      "text": "They drank and lowered their glasses.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 498.96,
      "end": 500.74,
      "text": "The fat man looked shrewdly at",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 500.8,
      "end": 501.48,
      "text": "Spade and asked:"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.66,
      "end": 502.98,
      "text": "\"You're a close-mouthed man?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 504.0,
      "end": 505.1,
      "text": "Spade shook his head.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 505.6,
      "end": 506.4,
      "text": "\"I like to talk.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 507.44,
      "end": 507.94,
      "text": "\"Better and better!\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 508.16,
      "end": 509.28,
      "text": "the fat man exclaimed."
    },
    {
      "start": 509.65,
      "end": 511.94,
      "text": "\"I distrust a close-mouthed man."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.3,
      "end": 514.76,
      "text": "He generally picks the wrong time to talk and"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.76,
      "end": 515.8,
      "text": "says the wrong things."
    },
    {
      "start": 516.07,
      "end": 517.8,
      "text": "Talking's something you can't do"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.81,
      "end": 520.0,
      "text": "judiciously unless you keep in practice."
    },
    {
      "start": 520.7,
      "end": 522.18,
      "text": "He beamed over his glass.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 523.18,
      "end": 523.64,
      "text": "\"We'll get along,"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.88,
      "end": 524.06,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.22,
      "end": 524.98,
      "text": "That we will."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.33,
      "end": 527.28,
      "text": "He set his glass on the table and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 527.38,
      "end": 529.7,
      "text": "held the box of Coronas del Ritz out to Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 530.26,
      "end": 530.58,
      "text": "\"A cigar,"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.74,
      "end": 530.94,
      "text": "sir.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 531.51,
      "end": 532.82,
      "text": "Spade took a cigar,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 533.06,
      "end": 533.94,
      "text": "trimmed the end"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.08,
      "end": 534.96,
      "text": "of it, and lighted it."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.06,
      "end": 535.16,
      "text": "Meanwhile"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.16,
      "end": 539.0,
      "text": "the fat man pulled another green plush chair around to face"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.12,
      "end": 542.02,
      "text": "Spade's within convenient distance and placed"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.02,
      "end": 544.46,
      "text": "a smoking-stand within reach of both chairs."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.18,
      "end": 547.28,
      "text": "Then he took his glass from the table,"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.88,
      "end": 549.14,
      "text": "took a cigar from the box,"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.64,
      "end": 550.64,
      "text": "and lowered himself into"
    },
    {
      "start": 550.76,
      "end": 551.22,
      "text": "his chair."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.32,
      "end": 555.14,
      "text": "His bulbs stopped jouncing and settled into flabby rest."
    },
    {
      "start": 555.44,
      "end": 557.56,
      "text": "He sighed comfortably and said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.0,
      "end": 558.36,
      "text": "\"Now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.46,
      "end": 558.7,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.88,
      "end": 560.34,
      "text": "we'll talk if you like."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.0,
      "end": 563.68,
      "text": "And I'll tell you right out that I'm a man who likes talking"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.94,
      "end": 565.26,
      "text": "to a man that likes to talk."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.92,
      "end": 566.46,
      "text": "\"Swell.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 567.14,
      "end": 568.56,
      "text": "Will we talk about the black bird?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 569.42,
      "end": 570.8,
      "text": "The fat man laughed and his",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 570.9,
      "end": 572.64,
      "text": "bulbs rode up and down on his laughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.62,
      "end": 573.94,
      "text": "\"Will we?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 574.14,
      "end": 576.08,
      "text": "he asked and, \"We will,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 576.66,
      "end": 577.02,
      "text": "he replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 577.62,
      "end": 579.0,
      "text": "His pink face"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.0,
      "end": 580.0,
      "text": "was shiny with delight."
    },
    {
      "start": 580.84,
      "end": 581.62,
      "text": "\"You're the man for me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.74,
      "end": 581.96,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.12,
      "end": 584.08,
      "text": "A man cut along my own lines."
    },
    {
      "start": 584.74,
      "end": 585.1,
      "text": "No beating"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.26,
      "end": 585.9,
      "text": "about the bush,"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.24,
      "end": 587.14,
      "text": "but right to the point."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.84,
      "end": 589.16,
      "text": "'Will we talk about the black bird?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.36,
      "end": 590.04,
      "text": "We will."
    },
    {
      "start": 590.59,
      "end": 591.44,
      "text": "I like that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.64,
      "end": 591.82,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 591.96,
      "end": 593.8,
      "text": "I like that way of doing business."
    },
    {
      "start": 594.17,
      "end": 596.56,
      "text": "Let us talk about the black bird by all means,"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.74,
      "end": 597.52,
      "text": "but first,"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.56,
      "end": 597.72,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.8,
      "end": 598.78,
      "text": "answer me a question,"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.88,
      "end": 599.2,
      "text": "please,"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.54,
      "end": 602.0,
      "text": "though maybe it's an unnecessary one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.9,
      "end": 603.26,
      "text": "so we'll"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.28,
      "end": 604.8,
      "text": "understand each other from the beginning."
    },
    {
      "start": 605.58,
      "end": 607.8,
      "text": "You're here as Miss O'Shaughnessy's representative?"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.376,
      "end": 612.26,
      "text": "Spade blew smoke above the fat man's head in a long",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 612.34,
      "end": 613.24,
      "text": "slanting plume."
    },
    {
      "start": 613.5,
      "end": 615.04,
      "text": "He frowned thoughtfully"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.2,
      "end": 616.88,
      "text": "at the ash-tipped end of his cigar."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.22,
      "end": 618.66,
      "text": "He replied deliberately:"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.9,
      "end": 620.58,
      "text": "\"I can't say yes or no."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.78,
      "end": 621.38,
      "text": "There's"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.52,
      "end": 623.18,
      "text": "nothing certain about it either way, yet.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 623.64,
      "end": 626.24,
      "text": "He looked up at the fat man and stopped frowning.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 626.7,
      "end": 627.08,
      "text": "\"It depends.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 628.48,
      "end": 629.63,
      "text": "\"It depends on—?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 629.97,
      "end": 631.28,
      "text": "Spade shook his head.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 631.52,
      "end": 633.26,
      "text": "\"If I knew what it depends on"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.4,
      "end": 634.34,
      "text": "I could say yes or"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.34,
      "end": 634.54,
      "text": "no.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 635.72,
      "end": 637.56,
      "text": "The fat man took a mouthful from his glass,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 637.74,
      "end": 638.24,
      "text": "swallowed it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.28,
      "end": 638.82,
      "text": "and suggested:"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.0,
      "end": 640.52,
      "text": "\"Maybe it depends on"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.62,
      "end": 641.22,
      "text": "Joel Cairo?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 641.44,
      "end": 642.9,
      "text": "Spade's prompt",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 643.12,
      "end": 643.64,
      "text": "\"Maybe\""
    },
    {
      "start": 643.84,
      "end": 644.88,
      "text": "was noncommittal."
    },
    {
      "start": 645.34,
      "end": 645.7,
      "text": "He drank.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 646.78,
      "end": 648.4,
      "text": "The fat man leaned forward until his",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 648.56,
      "end": 649.26,
      "text": "belly stopped him."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.4,
      "end": 651.7,
      "text": "His smile was ingratiating,"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.74,
      "end": 653.2,
      "text": "and so was his purring voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.22,
      "end": 654.8,
      "text": "\"You could say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.96,
      "end": 655.14,
      "text": "then,"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.2,
      "end": 656.28,
      "text": "that the question is"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.4,
      "end": 658.12,
      "text": "which one of them you'll represent?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 659.42,
      "end": 660.44,
      "text": "\"You could put it that way.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 661.6,
      "end": 663.0,
      "text": "\"It will be one or the other?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 663.9,
      "end": 664.74,
      "text": "\"I didn't say that.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 665.9,
      "end": 667.05,
      "text": "The fat man's eyes glistened.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 667.54,
      "end": 668.52,
      "text": "His voice sank to"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.6,
      "end": 669.22,
      "text": "a throaty whisper"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.36,
      "end": 669.66,
      "text": "asking:"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.84,
      "end": 671.5,
      "text": "\"Who else is there?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 672.64,
      "end": 674.38,
      "text": "Spade pointed his cigar at his own chest.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 675.392,
      "end": 675.7,
      "text": "\"There's me,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 675.92,
      "end": 676.46,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 677.64,
      "end": 680.62,
      "text": "The fat man sank back in his chair and let his body go flaccid.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 681.14,
      "end": 682.94,
      "text": "He blew his breath out in a long"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.04,
      "end": 683.82,
      "text": "contented gust."
    },
    {
      "start": 684.896,
      "end": 685.5,
      "text": "\"That's wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.7,
      "end": 685.94,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.04,
      "end": 686.52,
      "text": "he purred."
    },
    {
      "start": 686.68,
      "end": 687.38,
      "text": "That's wonderful."
    },
    {
      "start": 688.3,
      "end": 689.94,
      "text": "I do like a man that tells you right"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.94,
      "end": 691.42,
      "text": "out he's looking out for himself."
    },
    {
      "start": 692.736,
      "end": 693.18,
      "text": "Don't we all?"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.24,
      "end": 695.92,
      "text": "I don't trust a man that says he's not."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.82,
      "end": 699.54,
      "text": "And the man that's telling the truth when he says he's not"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.92,
      "end": 703.0,
      "text": "I distrust most of all, because he's an ass"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.66,
      "end": 706.52,
      "text": "and an ass that's going contrary to the laws of nature.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 707.488,
      "end": 708.62,
      "text": "Spade exhaled smoke.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 708.88,
      "end": 710.64,
      "text": "His face was politely attentive."
    },
    {
      "start": 710.98,
      "end": 711.4,
      "text": "He said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.56,
      "end": 712.16,
      "text": "\"Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 712.7,
      "end": 713.24,
      "text": "now let's talk"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.42,
      "end": 714.28,
      "text": "about the black bird.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 714.68,
      "end": 716.97,
      "text": "The fat man smiled benevolently.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 717.3,
      "end": 717.4,
      "text": "\"Let's,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 718.1,
      "end": 718.66,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 718.88,
      "end": 720.14,
      "text": "He squinted so"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.28,
      "end": 722.08,
      "text": "that fat puffs crowding together left"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.08,
      "end": 724.44,
      "text": "nothing of his eyes but a dark gleam visible."
    }
  ],
  "corrected": "claude"
}